00:01:16.109 --> 00:01:18.109
But I won't join the protest.

00:01:18.109 --> 00:01:19.109
Okay.

00:01:19.109 --> 00:01:22.109
So you won't stand in line in protest.

00:01:22.109 --> 00:01:26.109
