00:01:32.109 --> 00:01:35.109
We just need signatures.

00:01:35.109 --> 00:01:38.109
So far, everyone in the company has had it.

00:01:38.109 --> 00:01:42.109
Mark, I'm going to be straight with you.

00:01:42.109 --> 00:01:47.109
