00:01:57.739 --> 00:02:00.739
just sign the paper, Mark.

00:02:00.739 --> 00:02:11.669
Did he sign the paper?

00:02:11.669 --> 00:02:15.530
No.

00:02:15.530 --> 00:02:16.530
And you know why?

00:02:16.530 --> 00:02:20.530
At that moment, he said a silent prayer

00:02:20.530 --> 00:02:23.530
