00:02:23.530 --> 00:02:29.259
I commended him, and I reminded him that displaying courage now

00:02:29.259 --> 00:02:32.259
is going to help him in the future.

00:02:32.259 --> 00:02:33.259
Thanks, Luther.

00:02:33.259 --> 00:02:35.259
That's very encouraging to hear.

00:02:36.259 --> 00:02:39.259
Matthew, how do things go with you?

00:02:39.259 --> 00:02:45.550
Matthew, how do things go with you?

