00:04:17.839 --> 00:04:19.839
So what are you trying to say?

00:04:19.839 --> 00:04:34.139
Displaying courage now will help me display courage in the future.

00:04:34.139 --> 00:04:37.139
Well, I'm one of Jehovah's Witnesses,

