00:07:23.860 --> 00:07:29.259
No, I'm saying it because it's true.

00:07:29.259 --> 00:07:33.259
Being courageous doesn't mean we won't get nervous.

00:07:33.259 --> 00:07:37.259
Sometimes being courageous means taking action even though we are nervous.

00:07:37.259 --> 00:07:41.540
Thanks, that is encouraging.

00:07:41.540 --> 00:07:44.540
Here's a suggestion that may help.

00:07:44.540 --> 00:07:48.540
