00:07:48.540 --> 00:07:55.540
Based on that scripture, the next time you're about to face a situation that calls for courage,

00:07:55.540 --> 00:08:02.540
whether it be in the ministry or otherwise, tell yourself you just need to do these three things.

00:08:02.540 --> 00:08:09.920
Pray, open Jehovah and act.

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:11.920
You got it?

00:08:11.920 --> 00:08:17.920
Pray, open Jehovah and act.

00:08:17.920 --> 00:08:26.100
Wait till I'm going to write that down.

00:08:26.100 --> 00:08:30.100
Helping the friends address their fears, it's really going to help

00:08:30.100 --> 00:08:35.100
